Cross stitch kit for "The Raven" design.

This kit contains everything you need to make your own embroidered hoop:

1 x 6" wooden embroidery hoop;
1 x square 32 count ivory evenweave cloth (for stitching onto);
1 x square calico backing cloth (for finishing the hoop);
1 x length black stranded cotton embroidery thread;
2 x needles (in case you lose one!);
1 x little booklet of how to; and
1 x pattern sheet.

You will also need:

1 x pair sharp scissors;
1 x comfy place to sit;
Good lighting; 
Craft glue; and
Patience!

